parameters: \n<Aubrienne>Okay, that took some effort but we're on our way!
It is recommended to save before continuing.
This game only allows saving at certain points to help
avoid situations where progress is impossible.
If you feel like you've made a wrong move in battle,
hold down the 'R' key on your keyboard to restart it.
You can also restart the battle by pressing the Cancel
You can also flee from some battles using this menu.
Fleeing will return you to the beginning of the area.
It is recommended to restart battles before fleeing.
Don't let any of the party get knocked out! You'll
definitely be late for the Witch Moot if you have to
drag them all the way there!
